<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>Reset Your Password - {{appName}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .icon {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .icon svg {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      color: #dc2626;
    }
    .warning-box {
      background-color: #fef2f2;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .warning-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #991b1b;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .warning-box p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #7f1d1d;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #dc2626;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #b91c1c;
    }
    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .info-section {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info-section p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #dc2626;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        margin: 0;
        border-radius: 0;
      }
      .header {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üîê Reset Your Password</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 7a2 2 0 012 2m4 0a6 6 0 01-7.743 5.743L11 17H9v2H7v2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2.586a1 1 0 01.293-.707l5.964-5.964A6 6 0 1121 9z" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
        Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        We received a request to reset your password for your account at <strong>{{appName}}</strong>.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Click the button below to create a new password:
      </p>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button" target="_blank">Reset Password</a>
      </div>

      <div class="warning-box">
        <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice:</h3>
        <p>This password reset link will expire in <strong>1 hour</strong> for security reasons. If you don't reset your password within this time, you'll need to request a new reset link.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="info-section">
        <p><strong>üìß Account Details:</strong></p>
        <p>Email: {{userEmail}}</p>
        <p>Requested at: {{requestDate}}</p>
        <p>IP Address: {{ipAddress}}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="background-color: #fefce8; border-left: 4px solid #eab308; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #854d0e; margin: 0;">
          <strong>üîí Did you not request this?</strong>
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #854d0e; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
          If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your account remains secure. You may also contact our support team if you suspect any unauthorized activity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: #f0f9ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #1e40af; margin: 0;">
          <strong>üí° Tip:</strong> If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #3b82f6; margin: 10px 0 0 0; word-break: break-all;">
          {{resetLink}}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin: 0;">
          Remember your password? <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600;">Sign in to your account</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #999; margin: 0;">
          For security reasons, we never send passwords via email.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>¬© {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 5px;">
        You received this email because a password reset was requested for your account.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 5px;">
        <a href="{{supportUrl}}" style="color: #999;">Contact Support</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>